== Kinetic Request CE User Create
Creates a user and returns the username.

=== Parameters
[Error Handling]
  Determine what to return if an error is encountered.
[Space Slug]
  The Space the submission is being retrieved from (defaults to info value if not provided).
[Username]
  The unique username for the user.
[Password]
  The password for this user record.
[Space Admin]
  Should the user have space administration rights. (Yes / No)
[Email]
  The email address for this user record.
[Display Name]
  The display name for this user record.

=== Sample Configuration
Error Handling:   Error Message
Space Slug:       acme
Username:         test@example.com
Password:         secretPassword
Space Admin:      Yes
Display Name:     Jane Doe
Email:            test@example.com

=== Results
[Handler Error Message]
  Error message if an error was encountered and Error Handling is set to "Error Message".
[Username]
  The username of the created user record.

=== Detailed Description
This handler returns the username of the User record that was created.